<td>3 Miles </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-3'>
<th>Avg. Gradient</th>
<td>300 fpm</td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class='river-photo'>
<div class='controls'>
<h1>The Granite Gorge Section</h1>
</div>
